I lured him here.

79
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,640
I ran him over with the car.

80
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:22,640
Then I found a tool.

81
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,640
And beat him to death.

82
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:30,240
