85
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,440
Hello.

86
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:34,280
My sister asked me to come and pick up something.

87
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,760
She just went out.

88
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,280
